  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 09c0819852a80204586d7f9de68fa6d1, type: 3}
  m_Name: MindBetrayal
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalSO
  title: Sweet Temptress
  entry: I don't think I'll make it out. We've been lost down here for several days,
    but it finally set in.   Quinn went to look for a way out and came back to us
    claiming that the way out is through embracing the spirit  He looked mad and
    obsessed with her. We hid under a pile of bones in an open area- Quinn ran to
    the spirit.  He was "embraced" by her. His spirit was drained. He looked like
    a bag of skin with withered bones to fill the innards of the bag.
  number: 1
  image: {fileID: 0}
